text: "I'm Over You" is a 2000 song by English singer and actress Martine McCutcheon. It is the leading single from her second studio album Wishing. It went to number 2 in the United Kingdom, number 3 in Scotland and number 23 in Ireland. It was her second successful song in the United Kingdom following her 1999 single Perfect Moment. ==Track listings== UK CD single # "I'm Over You" (radio edit) – 3:42 # "I'm Over You" (Xenomania Club Mix) – 7:25 # "Perfect Moment" (Sleaze Sisters Anthem Mix) – 7:30 UK cassette single :A1.
